    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/karl_marlantes_506342",
        "quote": "And I think that it's - the military has actually made improvements, so people are considering post-traumatic stress disorder as, at the least, a possible psychological problem. You know, when I was in Vietnam, it was just considered malingering. And we're making progress.",
